WEBVTT

00:00:39.248 --> 00:00:41.891
Oof, difficult, isn't it?

00:00:42.411 --> 00:00:45.636
Well, this is an incredible number

00:00:45.660 --> 00:00:49.365
that will again take your breath away:

00:00:49.389 --> 00:00:50.601
seven.

00:00:50.625 --> 00:00:51.943
Seven what?

00:00:51.967 --> 00:00:56.053
Seven million premature deaths a year

00:00:56.077 --> 00:01:01.262
caused by exposure to the bad quality
of the air we breathe.